            "title": "足智彩｜新投注項目「開出角球讓球」 2月28日開始受注",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"新投注項目「開出角球讓球」，2月28日開始受注。足智彩\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/faea8f1e2adf3f89c2d7598617ce6b18/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250221/_2025022116205972550.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">新投注項目「開出角球讓球」，2月28日開始受注。足智彩</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>足智彩將於2 月28日賽事起，推出兩項全新投注種類，包括「開出角球讓球」及「加時開出角球讓球」。「開出角球讓球」結合「開出角球大細」及「讓球」的玩法，投注人士可選擇經「角球讓球數」調整後預計會開出較多角球數的主隊或客隊，並將「角球讓球數」對比法定比賽時間的全場開出角球賽果以確定注項。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d6c2a43c9ba75bf00b47838de0e61ae3/2025-02/chdc-ch.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
